OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776856004
OL,3,CPedestrian dies after being hit by a
OL,4,Ccar in early hours
OL,6,FA man in his 20s has died after being
OL,7,Fhit by a car on the A189 near
OL,8,FAnnitsford in the early hours of
OL,9,FSaturday (18 April).
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,12,Fstretch between Burradon Road and the
OL,13,FMoor Farm Roundabout shortly after
OL,14,F1.30am.
OL,16,FIt was reported that, for reasons yet
OL,17,Fto be established, a pedestrian was on
OL,18,Fthe northbound carriageway when he was
OL,19,Fstruck by a white Seat Alhambra.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
