FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776856004
OL,3,CPedestrian dies after being hit by a
OL,4,Ccar in early hours
OL,6,FThe pedestrian, a man in his 20s, was
OL,7,Ftaken to the Royal Victoria Infirmary
OL,8,Fin Newcastle for treatment of life-
OL,9,Fthreatening injuries. He died later on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,FHis next of kin have been informed and
OL,13,Fcontinued to be supported by officers.
OL,15,FThe driver of the Seat remained at the
OL,16,Fscene to assist police with enquiries.
OL,17,FThe road remained closed until around
OL,18,F11am on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
