FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776856004
OL,3,CPedestrian dies after being hit by a
OL,4,Ccar in early hours
OL,6,FOfficers from Northumbria Police's
OL,7,FRoads Policing Unit have appealed for
OL,8,Fwitnesses as part of their
OL,9,Finvestigation. They are especially
OL,10,Fkeen to hear from anyone with CCTV or
OL,11,Fdashcam footage of the incident itself
OL,12,For the moments leading up to the
OL,13,Fcollision.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776856004
OL,3,CPedestrian dies after being hit by a
OL,4,Ccar in early hours
OL,6,FSgt Steven Chappell of Northumbria
OL,7,FPolice said: "Our thoughts are with
OL,8,Fthe man's family and loved ones at
OL,9,Fthis incredibly difficult time. I
OL,10,Fwould like to express my heartfelt
OL,11,Fcondolences following this tragic
OL,12,Fincident, and we will continue to
OL,13,Fsupport them in any way that we can."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
