OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776856004
OL,3,CPedestrian dies after being hit by a
OL,4,Ccar in early hours
OL,6,FSgt Chappell added: "A range of
OL,7,Fenquiries are under way as we look to
OL,8,Festablish exactly what happened in the
OL,9,Fmoments leading to this collision. As
OL,10,Fpart of this, we are keen for any
OL,11,Fmotorists or witnesses who were
OL,12,Ftravelling in the area at this time to
OL,13,Fcome forward.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
